  <brief_title>Trial of Zesteem (Estradiol) in Healing of Split Thickness Skin Graft Donor Sites</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double Blind, Placebo Controlled Trial to Investigate the Efficacy of Zesteem (Estradiol) in Accelerating the Healing of Split Thickness Skin Graft Donor Sites.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Renovo</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Renovo</source>
  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial will assess the effects of Zesteem (estradiol) on the healing of split thickness
      skin graft donor sites in patients aged 18-85 years.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
